  Kau3-ui7 Lim5 tiuN2-lo2-niu5 kap Hui7-bi2, sim-pu7 Soat-mui5 saN e5 long2 tu2 teh choe3 am3-si5 e5 ka-teng5 le2-pai3, nng7 e5 sun-a2 long2 teh khun3 lah. Na7-si7 in lai7-bin7 u7 chit8 e5 tng5-kang thau5 kio3 choe3 Siu2-jin5 tu2 chhut-khi3 bo5 ti7-teh. Hut-jian5 hit ji7-saN-chap8 lang5 tui3 toa7-mng5 jip8--lai5. Bo5-hun bo5-hoe7 tit8-tit8 long3 kau3 toa7-thiaN, toa7-siaN chiu7 jiang2 kong2 u7 lang5 ti7-teh a2-bo5? Hui7-bi2 chhut-lai5 khoaN3, chai si7 chit8 e5 kun-jin5 su7-koaN, au7-bin7 khoaN3 chit8-tui lang5. Mng7 kong2 chiah am3 si7 beh chhong3 sim2-mih8? Hit e5 lang5 in3 kong2 “Thoan5-tiuN2 TiuN chiong-kun u7 su7 ai3 chhiaN2 Hui7-bi2 sio2-chia2 khi3 hoe7-bian7.” TiuN2-lo2-niu5 kap Soat-mui5 ti7 pin5-au7 thiaN chit8-e7 toa7 kiaN chhut-lai5 khoaN3. KhoaN3 tioh8 hiah che7 lang5, koh si7 am3-si5 Siu2-jin5 ia7 bo5 ti7-teh. Na7-si7 Hui7-bi2 chin ho2-taN2 toa7-siaN kap i kong2: “Goa2 si7 chit8 e5 lu2-chu2 na2-li2 kap Thoan5-tiuN2 chiong-kun u7 koan-he7? I ho5-pit8 tioh8 kap goa2 hoe7-bian7. Goa2 ia7 bo5 pit-iau3 kap i hoe7-bian7. Goa2 peng7-bo5 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3.” Lau7-bu2 tiuN2-lo2-niu5 kiaN kau3 khu7-khu7 chun3, chhui3-e7-tau2 khok8-khok8 hou3, chin kho2-lin5 kui7 loh8 kiu5 Siong7-te3 po2-hou7. Chit8-bin7 kiu5 hit e5 su7-koaN chhiu2 giah8-koan5, tauh-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8 su7? Hit e5 su7-koaN chin siu7-khi3 toa7 siaN hoah kong2, “Kio3 li2 lai5 khi3 chiu7 lai5 khi3,” hoah lang5 chhah chiuN7 kio7. Lang5 chiu7 tui3 Hui7-bi2 tit8-tit8 chhah chhut-khi3. Su7-koaN tui3 io-nih8 thiu-chhut te2-chheng3 hoah kong2 “Tiam7-tiam7 m7-chun2 khui-siaN soan-jiang2 hoah-kiu3. Na7 khui-siaN jiang2 chiu7 beh khui-chheng3 phah-si2.” Lim5 tiuN2-lo2-niu5 khui-siaN khau3, “KiaN2 ah! Kiu5 Siong7-te3 po2-hou7 kap li2 khi3.” Hui7-bi2 thiaN lau7-bu2 ai-kio3 thi5-khau3 e5 siaN, oat8-thau5 kong2, “A-bu2 m7-bian2 hoan5-lo2 choe3 li2 pang3-sim, goa2 tek-khak kau3-si2 siu2 Chu2 e5 to7-li2.” Hui7-bi2 hou7 lang5 chhah jip8 kio7, kio7-mng5 kio7-thang long2 koaiN-khi3 ka-teng kng teh long7. Lau7-bu2 chu7 an2-ni be7 kou3-tit to2-to2 loh8 khi3. Ah! Chham2-ah! Tiong7-hu si2, kiaN2 si2, cha-bou2-kiaN2 hou7 lang5 liah8 khi3. Soat-mui5 khoaN3 ta-ke to2-to2 loh8 khi3, pang5-nih8 nng7 e5 gin2-na2 thiaN-kiN3 hiah che7 lang5 ti7 lai7-bin7 kiuh-kiuh jiang2, kiaN cheng-sin5 ia7 khau3 be-be. Sio2-kou iu7 hou7 lang5 nge7 kng-khi3, sim loan7 chhau-chhau, iu7 m7-kaN2 jiang2. Kau3 lang5 long2 chhut-khi3 liau2 chiah hoah kiu3 lang5. Chhu3-piN tai7-ke ia7 chin kiaN, sui5-lang5 kou3 ka-ti7, bo5 su7 te7-it ho2. Si5-kan ia7 oa2 chiaN5 poaN3 mi5 lah, kai-chai3 chhu3-au7 u7 chit8 hou7 hoe7-iu2 tai7-ke khah tang5-sim, kin2 chau2 lai5 khoaN3, khoaN3 tioh8 an2-ni chit8-bin7 tau3-kiu3 tiuN2-lo2-niu5. Chit8-bin7 kin2 kio3 lang5 khi3 po3 Bok8-su chai. Bok8-su ti7 bin5-chhng5 chhia khi2--lai5 kin2 thong-ti si3-ui5 e5 hoe7-iu2 long2 giah8 thui5-a2 jiok chhut-khi3. 
  Tu2-gu7 Siu2-jin5 chhut-khi3, au7-lai5 chiah chai si7 khi3 sun5 chhan5-chui2, giah8 chit8 ki ti5-thau5 tui3 hng7-hng7 teh lai5, tai7-khai3 si7 siuN7 kong2 chhan5-chui2 long2 sun5-liau2 beh koah tiu7-a2 e5 si5 chit8 e5 lang5 choe3 chit8 pian3 eng7 chhiam-taN taN tit 4 taN3 chhek. Si3-pah goa7 kin, oa2 500 kin lat8. Kui2 e5 lang5-a2 oa2 lai5 i bo5 lun2--tioh8, koh u7 oh8 kun5-thau5, kha-chhiu2 chin ho2. Goeh8 hou7 hun5 kham3-leh, goeh8-kng hoan2-ou hoan2-ou. KhoaN3 thau5-cheng5 chit8-tin7 lang5 kng chit8-teng2 kio7, kng-teh-chhek8, poaN3-kau2-chau2. In m7-kaN2 kng tui3 toa7-be2-lou7, si7 chau2 tui3 sio2-lou7-a2, chiah e7 hiah tu2-ho2 kap Siu2-jin5 sio cheng-thau5. Siu2-jin5 ia7 put-kai2 ki5-i3 ian5-lou7 gim5-si choe3 phoaN7 bo5-lam7-bo5-lam7 kin2 gim5 kin2-kiaN5. Kio7-lai7 Hui7-bi2 jin7-tit si7 Siu2-jin5 e5 siaN am3-am3 hoaN-hi2, ki5-to2 Chu2 pang-chan7, ng3-bang7 u7 kiu3. Tiam7-tiam7 m7-kaN2 chhut-siaN. ThiaN gim5-si e5 siaN na2-kin7, chiu7 chai Siu2-jin5 i2-keng oa2 lai5 kau3 sin-piN, hut-jian5 tui3 kio7-lai7 toa7-siaN kio3, “Siu2-jin5 kin2 lai5 kiu3 goa2.” Siu2-jin5 jin7-tit si7 Hui7-bi2 e5 siaN koh khoaN3 su7-koaN choe3 cheng5 kiaN5, chit8 pou7 hun7 e5 lang5 i2-keng chau2 chin3-cheng5. In-ui7 Hui7-bi2 chin gau5, Siong7-te3 hou7 i u7 ti3-sek, tui3 thiaN Siu2-jin5 gim5-si e5 siaN hit-si5, i ti7 kio7-lai7 thiau-ti5 ngiauh8-ngiauh8-tang7, kio7 io5-lai5, io5-khi3, u7 si5 giong7-giong7 beh peng2-kio7, kng kio7 e5 si7 ka-teng koh m7-si7 kio7-hu, bo5 koan3-si3, kio3-khou2 lian5-thian. Sou2-i2 su7-koaN kap chit8 pou7-hun7 e5 peng long2 chau2 chin3-cheng5 khi3. Chhun chit8 pou7-hun7 ka-teng kou3 kio7 chau2 ban7 sui5 ti7 kio7-au7. Siu2-jin5 thiaN Hui7-bi2 sio2-chia2 teh kio3 i, chek-si5 kam2-kak si7 pang2-hui2 liah8 lang5, i si7 m7-chai Khun-hong kap in bo2-ku7 teh piN3-kui2. Siu2-jin5 e5 tit8-kam2 si7 pang2-hui2 liah8 lang5 beh kong3 hoan-thau5. Che ia7-si7 TiuN chiong-kun cha2 choe3 lek8-lim5 pang2-siu2 e5 ku7-thng-thau5. Siu2-jin5 chek-si5 chau2-oa2 siong3 cheng-cheng t