  Chiah kong2 Siu2-jin5 chhoa7 Hui7-bi2 chu7 an2-ni thau3-mi5 chau2. Jit8--si5 bih, am3-si5 chau2, tit8-tit8 chau2-kau3 Hun5-lam5 seng2-siaN5. Khi3 bih ti7 Siu2-jin5 chhin-chhek e5 tau. In si7 choe3-sit lang5, si7 jiat8-sim e5 Ki-tok-tou5. Toa3 ti7 li7 siaN5 chiaN5 phou3-lou7 chit8 e5 phian-phiah-e5 hiuN-chng e5 sio2 tek-ui5-a2 lai7. Sou2-i2 bo5 hiah khoai3 hoat-kian3 tioh8. 
  TaN hiah-e5 peng-a2 chu7 an2-ni thoa sin-si, kap kng tng7-kha, tng7-chhiu2 tioh8-siong--e5 to3-khi3. Peng-a2 chau2 khi3 peng-iaN5 po3 si2. Ka-teng to3-khi3 soa3 m7-kaN2 jip8-khi3. Chhu3-nih8 lang5-kheh kong7-kong7-kun2. Khun-hong le2-hok8 chheng7 pian7-pian7, kau3 beh tau3 lah tai7-ke chiah chai si7 beh chhoa7 sin-niu5. Tit8-tit8 tan2, khoaN3-si5 beh chin3-pang5, si5 ia7 koe3 lah, sin-niu5 kau3-taN iau2-boe7 lai5. Tai7-ke am7-kun2 chhun tng5-tng5, long2 hong-siaN Tan5--ka e5 siau3-ia5 beh chhoa7-chhin. Chiah che7-hoe3 chiah beh chhoa7, chit-pai2 siu3-kiu5 si7 chhin chhiu2 pha--e5. Liah8 in bo2-ku7 TiuN chiong-kun choe3 moai5-lang5--e5. Un2-tang3 chin-sui2, na7 m7-si7 u7 Goat8-li2 Siong5-gou5 e5 pan7, ia7 tioh8 u7 Sai3 Se-si e5 khoan2. Na7 bo5 “Siu-hoa pi3-goat8 e5 sui2, ma7 u7 tim5-hi5 lok8-gan7 e5 sui2.”（Na7 bo5 hoe khoaN3 i lai5 kian3-siau3 chiu7 hap8 khi3, goeh8-niu5 khoaN3 i lai5 chiu7 ng-bin7 e5 sui2, ia7 tek-khak u7 li2-hi5 khoaN3 i lai5 e5 sui2 chiu7 chhang3 loh8 chui2, gan7 teh poe khoaN3 i lai5 e5 sui2 chiu7 hioh loh8--lai5 e5 sui2). Ji5-chhiaN2 ke3-chng m7-chai beh kah goa7 che7 lai5 leh. Sou2-i2 jin5-san jin5-hai2 e5 lang5 ai3 lai5 khoaN3. Iu7-koh si7 5 goeh8 13 jit8, siaN5-lai7 ngia5 Seng5-hong5, hong-siaN pong3-iaN2 pi2 beh lai5 khoaN3 toa7-hi3 e5 lang5 iau2 khah che7. Khun-hong ia7 iong5-iong5 tek-i3 chhun-hong moa2-bin7, chit8 tiam2 tan2 koe3 chit8 tiam2 tan2 bo5. Tan2 kau3 bak8-chiu seN bi2-lo5-a2, sim-lai7 chian tiN-koe2. Chit8-choa7 chhut, chit8-choa7 jip8, mng5-teng7 tah8 kau3 beh ui-khi3. Lang5-kheh tan2 kau3 toa7-tng5 ko3 sio2-tng5. Kou-put-chiong in bo2-ku7 hoah khui-toh. In bo2-ku7 sim-te2 am3-am3 teh siuN7 poh-kaN2 e7 chhut-su7. Bo5, an2-choaN2 e7 bu2 kau3 chiah oaN3. Chit8-sim siuN7 kong2 sim-pak e5 su7-koaN kap iaN5-lai7 e5 oe7-peng khi3, che si7 siang7 tho3-tong3 un2-tang3 e7 sun7-su7 chiah tioh8. M7-ku2 eng3-kai boe7 tau3, m7-si7, si7 ai3 koh khah-cha2 tioh8 kau3-ui7 chiah tioh8. M7, kiam2-si7 siuN-oaN3 he7 chhiu2, m7, kiam2-si7 lou7-ti