  Lim5 tiuN2-lo2-niu5 thiaN Bok8-su to3-khi3 sou2 kong2 e5 siau-sit, chai Hui7-bi2 siu7 Siu2-jin5 kiu3 khi3 chiu7 kui2-hun khah an-sim. Tai7-ke kiu5 Chu2 pang-chan7 in2-chhoa7, ng3-bang7 e7 sun7-su7. Chong2-si7 phah-si2 lang5 chit8 tiau5 beng7-an3 tek-khak e7 u7-su7, tui3 chit-chan5 tai7-ke chin khoa3-lu7. TiuN chiong-kun theng3-hau7 tai7-ke soaN3-sek8 au7, chin siu7-khi3 kio3 hiah e5 ka-teng lai5, seng3 hoat tin5-tiau5 giah8 khi2--lai5 tit8 but8. Chiok-chham2 tioh8 siong bo5 lang5 kho2-lin5 koh hou7 lang5 but8. Chiong5-tiong khah lau7-poe3 e5 chhau3-thau5-a2-chek hou7 lang5 but8 siong7 thiam2. I siau3-lian5 ia7-si7 chit8 e5 lou5-moa5. TiuN chiong-kun me7 i an2-ni si7 chin “sit-hong”（sit-hong = Iu2--e5 choe3-su7 sit-loh8 hong-thau5, bo5 the2-bian7). An2-choaN2 iam2-ki5 sit-kou2, na2 iap-boe2 kau2 boe2-a2 iap-leh, bin7 ti3 kah-hah8, an2-ni soe-soe-a to3-lai5. Sit-liau2 goa2 pun2 chiong-kun e5 ui-hong. Khi3 kau3 bo5 ho2 kho2-jim2, chiong chiaN5 chap8 e5 ka-teng tiap8 tit chit8 tiuN5 lok8-hoa liu5-sui2 chhi-chham2 lok8-phek. Khau3-khou2 lian5-thian, oan3-siaN su3-khi2. Chhoa7 sin-niu5 e5 jit8 soa3 piN3 choe3 loan7 chhau-chhau thi5-khau3 e5 jit8. Chiong-kun but8 lang5 chhiu2 kaN2-si7 sng lah, tin5-tiau5 pang3-leh, jip8--lai5 chhiu2 tui3 toh-teng2 toa7-e7 chiu7 tng3 loh8 khi3, toa7-siaN hoah-kong2 na7 bo5 liah8 chit e5 loh8-kau3-a2-kui2 lai5 chek-kut tek-khak bo5 beh pang3 i kan-hiu. Keh jit8 chek-si5 chhe lang5 lai5 Su7-liong5 tiau-cha. Lai5 bo5 poaN3 lang5, chai tiuN2-lo2-niu5 kap sim-pu7 iau2 ti7-teh, hian7-si5 khi3 ti7 pai3-tng5. U7 soan-kau3-su po2-hou7, si7 cha-bou2 lang5, kap che su7 ia7 bo5 siang-kan. Iau3-kin2 si7 ai3 liah8 Siu2-jin5 kap Hui7-bi2. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 si3-ke3 am3-hong2. Goan5-in ui7-tioh8 si7 su-su7, lam7-iong7 kun-ui, chit-koan5 lai5 jia2-su7, sou2-i2 m7-kaN2 hian2-jian5 tui-chhip. M7-na7 phai3-lang5 si3-koe3 am3-hong2, chiu7 Khun-hong ia7 si5-khi3 Chioh8-iu5 kong-si e5 thau5-lou7 si3-ke3 lok8-lok8 kiaN5, be7 su sit-khi3 ka-ti7 chhui3-nih beh chia