  Si5-jit8 chin khoai3-koe3 liam-piN koe3 poaN3-ni5 khah ke, ni5-te2 kau3 lah chin kin7 chiok Seng3-tan3 e5 si5, Siu2-jin5 jit8--si5 m7-kaN2 chhut-khi3. Am3-si5 chiu7 khi3 chit8-keng hun2-chhiuN2 choe3 kang. Hui7-bi2 ia7 m7-bat chhut-khi3, siong5-siong5 si7 ti7 lai7-bin7 pang-bang5 ke-lai7 su7. U7 chit8-jit8 thau3-cha2 Hui7-bi2 beh chhut-khi3 se2-saN. Chhiu2 phang5 chit8 bin7-thang2 saN tui3 au7-boe2-mng5 chhut-khi3, beh khi3 au7-piah khe-a2. Hut-jian5 taN thau5 chit8 khoaN3 toa7 tioh8-kiaN. Che si7 bin5-bang7 a2-si7 chin-chiaN3, chiu7-si7 Khun-hong chhiu2 hiahN chit8-nia2 toa7 hiu5, bin7 chin siau-san2 khia7 ti7 i e5 bin7-cheng5. Hui7-bi2 kiaN chit8 e7 sin5-put-hu7 the2, saN piaN tiam3 thou5-kha oat8-thau5 chu7 an2-ni piaN3 teh chau2. 
  Khun-hong khoaN3 chit8-e7 ia7 na2-chun2 tui3 bang7-tiong kiaN-chhiN2, toa7-hiu5 hiat-kak8 khui-pou7 tit8-jiok. Bian2 kui2 pou7 chiu7 hou7 i jiok tioh8. Hia si7 phian-phiah-e5 hiuN-chng thau3-cha2 lang5 chin-chio2, si3-piN long2 bo5 lang5. Ki3-jian5 hou7 i jiok-tioh8, Hui7-bi2 chiu7 tong3-tiam7, thau5-khak chhih-chhih kiong2-chhiu2, bak8-chiu kheh-kheh ki5-to2. I e5 sim-lai7 siuN7 kong2 chham2-lah, hai2 sui-bong2 khoah-khoah, chun5-thau5 eh8-eh8, ku2 ia7 e7 sio-tng7. TaN ti7 chia iu7-koh tng7 tioh8 i. Lau2-sit8 kong2 i tui3 Khun-hong peng7 m7-si7 phaiN2-i3. Si7 m7-ke3 bo5 siang7 sin3-giong2 e5 lang5, koat-sim ai3 siu2 lau7-pe7 e5 ui5-gian5. Chit8 sim ia7 si7 chin thiaN3--i, m7-ku2 na7 siuN7 tioh8 i na2 pang2-hui2 eng7 nge7-liah8--e5 sit8-chai7 chin m7-goan7. Ia7 siuN7 ui7 chit chan5 su7 jia2-khi2 mia7-an3, taN chit pai2 hou7 i tu2-tioh8 m7-chai beh chaiN2-iuN7? Sim-lai7 ia7 siu7-khi3, ia7 kiaN-hiaN5, ia7 thiaN3--i. Sit8-chai7 si7 chit8 e5 kho2-ai3 e5 tek8-jin5, be7-hiau2 kong2 e5 sim-cheng5. Chi2-u7 bak8-chiu pang3-kheh ki5-to2 kau-tai3 Chu2. Phah-sng3 kau3 chia chit tiau5 beng7-an3 phoa3 lah. Tai7-khai3 Khun-hong e7 chin siu7-khi3, e7 thoa i khi3 kiN3-koaN. Bo5 phah-sng3 u7 sio-lo7 e5 chui2 tih ti7 i e5 kha-poaN5. Koh u7 teh hau2 chheh-khui3 e5 siaN. Hui7-bi2 bak8-chiu thau thi2-khui ka7 i khoaN3-mai7, chiah chai Khun-hong e5 chiaN3-kha chit8-kha kui7 ti7 thou5-kha, chhiu2 ng-bin7 teh hau2, tih ti7 i e5 kha-poaN5 sio-sio e5 chui2 m7-si7 chui2, si7 Khun-hong e5 bak8-sai2, chin ku2 nng7 e5 lang5 bo5 kong2-oe7. Au7-lai5 Hui7-bi2 tui3 chhiu2 ka7 i khan khi2-lai5. Khun-hong taN-thau5 khoaN3 Hui7-bi2 kam5-bak8-sai2 e5 bin7. Khun-hong lian5 siaN kiu5 “Hui7-bi2 sio2-chia2 chhiaN2 li2 sia3-bian2, hou7 li2 siu7 kiaN, hou7 li2 phun-pho, goan7 li2 sia3-bian2.” Hui7-bi2 khoaN3 Khun-hong e5 thai3-tou7 m7-si7 beh lai5 tui-chhip i, si7 ho2-i3 lai5 chhoe7 i, sim chiah siu7 an-ui3. Tui3 an2-ni bin7 tng2-chhio3. Khun-hong khoaN3 Hui7-bi2 tng2-chhio3 chiah khi2--lai5, khan Hui7-bi2 e